// bbCodePress
//
// bbcode include list (simple)
//
// new line      = (bbcode=br)
// divider image = (bbcode=ibr)
// quick keys are NOT required, leave blank
// $0 = selected text (or cursor if none)

// bbcode id, name (help text), codes, image, quick key
b,bold,[b]$0[/b],bold.gif,ctrl+b
u,underline,[u]$0[/u],underline.gif,ctrl+u
i,italic,[i]$0[/i]',italic.gif,ctrl+i
ibr
url,link,[url]$0[/url],href.gif,ctrl+h
img,image,[img]$0[/img],image.gif,ctrl+p
ibr
code,code,[code]$0[/code],code.gif,shift+ctrl+c
quote,quote,[quote]$0[/quote],quote.gif,shift+ctrl+q
